Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that weird to walk around town\Non Christmas with Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I try to visualize it,\Nweird things keep happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, it's been so cold\Non the second floor of the gym,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so we haven't been going up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to spend special time alone with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hey, on Christmas..."\NAnd to make that happen, I figured\Nthe best bet would be Christmas, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And to make that happen, I figured\Nthe best bet would be Christmas, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hey, on Christmas..."\NThe problem would be to actually\Nask her to hang out on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem would be to actually\Nask her to hang out on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I just wrote it extra hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but even after I erased it,\Nyou could still see her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of like when I close my eyes\Nto sleep, and even when tomorrow comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forget about Shimamura
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Christmas"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,from the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever Shimamura asks me to do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how much I'd end up complying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:03:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wrong mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Would I try? I probably would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a nap together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so wrapped up with trying to ask\NShimamura to hang out on Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I almost went off the edge,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,climbed up a tree,\Nand can't come back down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there, Shimako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. What? Do I need a reason\Nto talk to my buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo. Studying hard, Adacchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you are? Wow, how studious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Alrighty! Let's go to Nagafuji's place today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't shake the feeling that you end up\Nnear our {\i1}kotatsu {\i0}like every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, you're just imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait. My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Wait, how is that any different?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll just keep thinking about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what were you trying to ask me, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Hey, on Christmas..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's study together... or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Study? Then we should invite\NHino and Nagafuji, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're smarter than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means they'd get nothing\Nout of studying with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. You think that\Nour grades are about the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're about the same level of stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I'm kidding. Sure.\NWhy don't we study together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we study? The library?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe a family restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At home! At your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's really dusty, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your room, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about my place...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, that would be\Na bit awkward for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, sure. Let's go to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's dusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, a friend. Whoa, in our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Whoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, was it? Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.09,0:06:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for letting me come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't your room this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. My study room is upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Parakeety"   "Croquette"   "Li'l Cutlet"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, none of these are doing it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you say how you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, how about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely the next mascot\Nfor the Nagafuji Butcher Shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Nagafuji Butcher Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely the next mascot\Nfor the Nagafuji Butcher Shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Li'l Croquette, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess that'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean, "That's the one"?\NYou even gave her a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:07:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll give you a treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet! Wait, is it another\Nkiss on the forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, yeah... I guess I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Auntie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have mandarins, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Close... Are we close?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not any more than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we get along like normal friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you it was dusty.\NThis is my study room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Until things warm up, I call for a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you usually listen to music\Nwhile you study, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, pretty often.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,On Ch... Chri...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what kind of kid were you, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Pretty normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I was always the kid\Nserving lunch to the other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I think my hair was shorter,\Nand not dyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura with short hair... With black hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you like, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! I, uh... haven't really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:09:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... I picture you holding\Nthe preschool teacher's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what were you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was, uh... I'm particular\Nabout whose hand I hold...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck am I saying?!\NNow I sound like I'm asking her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... I wonder why you hold mine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh, earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura had asked why it was her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? It's rather simple, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to just come out and say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd basically be saying,\N"I love you, Shimamura."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If she woke up and you were kissing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd really be game over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not like I\Nabsolutely need to kiss her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I wouldn't be opposed\Nif Shimamura asked for one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But she didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I was just--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is much softer and pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A-Ah, I shee...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you a little sleepyhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Shimamura... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Chri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you usually do on Christmas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We get fried chicken for dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My little sister still believes\Nin Santa Claus, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How long did you believe in Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? I didn't, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way a nice old man\Nlike that actually exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:12:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought... he was at my preschool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's because the only people to ever\Ntalk about Santa were at my preschool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we both sorta sucked at childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know... I think we were dumber\Nand more uninhibited when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing we survived at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice. Probably never experienced\Nstiff shoulders back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I just want to stay\Nlike this with Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'm protecting my precious\Nchild with my wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi's been acting weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel her staring at me a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first weird thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The second thing is when we're talking,\Nshe seems to always be holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how her lips haven't cramped yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And the third thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She scored higher on\Nour English test than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the third thing has\Nnothing to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ow...\N--Huh? Shimamura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! Actually, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just having a little bit of fun.\NMore importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, take a deep breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Adacchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer if you didn't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear not. I probably won't use\Nthat nickname again. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just been wondering what's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this winter... I mean, next week, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In about ten days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten days?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got this, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you after I think on it some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a girl I was really close\Nwith in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She would always hide behind me and\Nto put it simply, she was like Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is when I was still unguarded,\Nstill had interest in everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and dove headfirst into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She really loved sparkly things\Nlike marbles and wind chimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only when she found sparkly things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that she'd leave my side and run towards them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at the image\Ntrending on social media today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--You got your lunch bag?\N--Oh? They both have their hands raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yup. Bye!\N--Oh? They both have their hands raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get to school, too, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shush your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,High schoolers only need to get to\Nschool before the sun goes up fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who taught you that dumb rule? Hurry and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:16:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis! Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend is here! That girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh... Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that came over the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How ya doin', Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Heyo... Mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to sound like a jock?\NSo, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit early, isn't it?\NActually, when did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:17:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to stop by somewhere...\NThis is pretty normal, and I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold, so let's talk inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Help her eat, would you? She's so slow,\NI just don't know what to do with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to say any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I ate at home, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... One bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to eat more!\NDoesn't your mom tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As a mom, you feel better when your\Ndaughter is a bit pudgy and doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,wither away worrying about her waistline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't. We don't really talk much.\NShe's rarely home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fanks for the grub.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go talk in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeesh, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I just turned the heater on,\Nso make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you that yesterday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go out somewhere... or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Sure... Wait, that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but after school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean like right now\Nand skip school, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not today... you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering about the 25th of this month!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The 25th? The 25th...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,December 25th... Oh, that 25th.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Christmas, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh--?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost asked her why, but I stopped myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why Christmas? Why with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I asked her why, I felt like\Nthe backbone of our relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,would get bent out of shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take a bunch of time\Nand effort to fix it later,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wondered if I'd even bother with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,though the answer was sadly pretty clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't really thought it out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what did you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't really thought it out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to think that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi never got to have\Nthe full Christmas experience
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why she asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, just looking at how she's\Nacting and how red her face is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's basically like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asking me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not a big deal or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... I think I just\Nmaybe wanted to hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with someone on a fun day like Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not maybe. I do want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She just wanted to hang out with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And she doesn't have any other friends,\Nso that's why she asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't have to be me specifically. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to be home by dinner,\Nbut if you're okay with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to decide where\Nwe're going to go and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wittle puppy Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We should get to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Right... Then let's go together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us hurry. Yes. Oh, I'm going to be so busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for li'l ol' me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I go all old timey?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:22:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me catch a ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I guess I'm hanging out\Nwith Adachi this Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 5: 'Adachi's Question'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not like Santa's coming by,\Neven if I waited at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 5: 'Adachi's Question'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'White Album'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'White Album'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: {\i1}Kotatsu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'White Album'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotatsu {\i0}tables just ruin everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'White Album'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.63,0:23:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.75,0:23:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I'm not leaving this warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the preview.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.34,0:24:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, too cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
